003e단맛에 이끌려 연거푸 들이마시다\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e결국 과거 날짜를 지나버려\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e집으로 내려갔다는 이야기가 전해지죠.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d38cxpfv0ljg7q.cloudfront.net/content_images/contents_images-1623411123405-%ED%86%A0%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%B43.JPG\"\u003e마을에 있는 수많은 소곡주와\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"\u003e토박이소곡주의 다른 점은 무엇인가요?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e우선 토박이소곡주에 들어가는 쌀은\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e제가 직접 농사 지은 쌀이에요.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e인위적으로 첨가한 단맛이 아닌 \u003cstrong\u003e쌀에서 나온 단맛\u003c/strong\u003e이죠.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e거기에 토박이소곡주에는 약간의 구절초를 첨가하여\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e은은한 꽃향\u003c/strong\u003e을 맡을 수 있다는 것이 특징입니다.\u003c/p\u003e","address":"충청남도 서천군 한산면 충절로 1148번길 13","imgUrl":"https://d38cxpfv0ljg7q.cloudfront.net/admin_contents/origin/u7Z7-1622700274371-to-bak-ee-so-gok-ju.png"},"paymentData":{"id":0,"merchantUid":"","status":"","baseAddress":"","detailAddress":"","zipCode":"","receiverName":"","deliveryComment":"","receiverPhoneNumber":"","receiverAddressId":0},"product":{"id":0,"content":"","mobileContent":"","discountPrice":0,"makerId":0,"name":"","originPrice":0,"productCategoryId":0,"sellingCount":0,"starCount":0,"starRating":"","status":"","subName":"","isDamhwaBox":0,"tasteStandard":"","deliveryPolicy":{"deliveryCompany":"","deliveryNote":"","id":0,"makerId":0,"minTotalForFreeDelivery":0,"name":"","noFreeSpecialDelivery":false,"regularDeliveryPrice":0,"separateDelivery":fals